# blocksalat

a modular synth out of blocks.

this is an experiment to use [blockly](https://www.npmjs.com/package/blockly) as a ui for [kabelsalat](https://kabel.salat.dev/learn/).

live at [block.salat.dev](https://block.salat.dev/)

## examples

- [modulated saw](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [multichannel](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [feedback](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [am](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [kick + snare](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [monoponic midi example](https://block.salat.dev/#) tested with [this strudel pattern](https://strudel.cc/#bigiMCAuLiA3Iikuc2NhbGUoIkM0Om1pbm9yIikuY2xpcCguNSkubWlkaSgp)
- [polyphonic midi example](https://block.salat.dev/#) tested with [this strudel pattern](https://strudel.cc/#bigiMCwxLDIsMyIpLmNob3JkKCI8RG03IEc3IENeNyBBN2I5PiIpLnZvaWNpbmcoKS5taWRpKCk%3D)
- [audio input + feedback](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- [custom blocks](https://block.salat.dev/#)
- feel free add your own by sending a PR :) i'll accept anything
